# Shadcn-Vue UI Components

## Componentes Disponibles

### Layout
- `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardTitle`, `CardDescription`, `CardContent`, `CardFooter`
- `Dialog`, `DialogTrigger`, `DialogContent`, `DialogHeader`, `DialogTitle`
- `Sheet`, `Drawer`
- `Tabs`, `TabsList`, `TabsTrigger`, `TabsContent`

### Formularios
- `Input`, `Textarea`, `Select`, `Checkbox`, `Switch`
- `Button` (variants: default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link)
- `Label`, `FormField`, `FormItem`, `FormLabel`, `FormMessage`

### Tablas
- `Table`, `TableHeader`, `TableBody`, `TableRow`, `TableHead`, `TableCell`

### Feedback
- `Alert`, `Badge`, `Progress`, `Skeleton`
- Toast: usar `vue-sonner` con `<Toaster />`

### Navegación
- `Sidebar`, `SidebarProvider`, `SidebarContent`, `SidebarGroup`
- `Breadcrumb`, `DropdownMenu`, `NavigationMenu`

## Patrones Comunes

### Card con Header y Acciones
```vue
<Card>
  <CardHeader>
    <CardTitle>Título</CardTitle>
    <CardDescription>Descripción</CardDescription>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    <!-- Contenido -->
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

### Tabla con Datos
```vue
<Table>
  <TableHeader>
    <TableRow>
      <TableHead>Columna</TableHead>
    </TableRow>
  </TableHeader>
  <TableBody>
    <TableRow v-for="item in items" :key="item.id">
      <TableCell>{{ item.value }}</TableCell>
    </TableRow>
  </TableBody>
</Table>
```

### Botones
```vue
<Button>Default</Button>
<Button variant="outline">Outline</Button>
<Button variant="destructive">Eliminar</Button>
<Button variant="ghost" size="sm">
  <Icon name="i-lucide-edit" class="h-4 w-4" />
</Button>
```

### Badge
```vue
<Badge>Default</Badge>
<Badge variant="secondary">Secondary</Badge>
<Badge variant="outline">Outline</Badge>
```

